{"tid":1674343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"準備買Call of Duty 既巴打一入來","createTime":"2019-10-25T07:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T08:23:30.000Z","uid":172772,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ebbf35020fab53e18ae0acdde88fe226758398ba","tid":1674343,"uid":172772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:07:02.000Z","msg":"10月8日，香港電競選手「聰哥」在《爐石戰記》大師職業賽獲勝之後的受訪中，戴上面罩高喊「光復香港，時代革命」。<br />\n<br />\n事後比賽主辦公司「暴雪娛樂」（Blizzard Entertainment，下簡稱「暴雪」）一度宣布沒收選手的競賽獎金，並禁賽一年。同時也解約兩名台灣主播賽評「易先生」與「偷米」，引發全球玩家抗議。10月12日，暴雪改為發回「聰哥」獎金、禁賽縮短為半年，但截至今日，並未收回解約主播與賽評的決定。在抗議事件中，該公司甚至一度用技術方法禁止玩家註銷帳號，造成更大的爭議。<br />\n<br />\n大家咁快唔記得暴雪做過咩啦？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果連抵制隻遊戲都做唔到，<br />\n仲學咩撚野人講光復香港時代革命!</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e3bd7bac11971c04c8bccf7a4a83715710c19a8f","tid":1674343,"uid":172772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9960ad97cead8769d09bf3c8902ef4c8d058ab0b","tid":1674343,"uid":7494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:07:28.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\nbtw, 唔好意思, 借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鍾庭耀發起全港大型民調及公投嘅眾籌post, 需要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n(代POST)【本土X國際戰線】鍾庭耀發起全港大型民調及公投<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659927</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌傳送門﹕<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTfsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=ac3e0a5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"95691b8174a08152dec0478f7d0402b93bbc64ce","tid":1674343,"uid":172772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:07:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c17402f726e9b312ac3ca3799f671217a2197687","tid":1674343,"uid":172772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited